<TITLE>
Tivaci, the Wolf god of the Chemehuevi tribe (Tipaci, Tivachi, Tevatsi)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Tivaci,
the Chemehuevi wolf figure.">
