">Coyote Tales of the Mojave Desert</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Coyote and Wolf stories from the Chemehuevi, Kawaiisu and Tubatulabal tribes.
<BR>

<IMG SRC="dot5.gif"  ALT="*"><b><A HREF="
http://escholarship.org/uc/item/1bt8j4z3;jsessionid=0A25994C05A20B17FAB99CE30D1A5FE1#page-1
">Chemehuevi Religious Beliefs and Practices</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Anthropology article on the mythology and ritual life of the Chemehuevi people.
